.toArray(new Method[0]);\\n   }\\n}\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1777858111789}]}\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.jboss.arquillian.test:arquillian-test-spi:1.1.10.Final/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-04T01-29-51-720954Z.log:1338:[tool-call] delta {\"path\":\"tests/src/org.jboss.arquillian.test/arquillian-test-spi/1.1.10.Final/src/test/java/org_jboss_arquillian_test/arquillian_test_spi/SecurityActionsTest.java\",\"content\":\"/*\\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\\n *\\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\\n */\\npackage org_jboss_arquillian_test.arquillian_test_spi;\\n\\nimport static org.assertj.core.api.Assertions.assertThat;\\n\\nimport org.jboss.arquillian.test.spi.SecurityActionsInvoker;\\nimport org.jboss.arquillian.test.spi.TestClass;\\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\\n\\npublic class SecurityActionsTest {\\n    @Test\\n    void loadsClassesAndCreatesInstancesThroughSecurityActions() {\\n        ClassLoader originalContextClassLoader = Thread.currentThread().getContextClassLoader();\\n        String testClassName = TestClass.class.getName();\\n\\n        try {\\n            Thread.currentThread().setContextClassLoader(TestClass.class.getClassLoader());\\n            assertThat(SecurityActionsInvoker.loadClass(testClassName)).isSameAs(TestClass.class);\\n\\n            Thread.currentThread().setContextClassLoader(new HidingClassLoader(TestClass.class.getClassLoader(), testClassName));\\n            assertThat(SecurityActionsInvoker.loadClass(testClassName)).isSameAs(TestClass.class);\\n\\n            TestClass created = SecurityActionsInvoker.newInstance(\\n                    testClassName,\\n                    new Class<?>[] {Class.class},\\n                    new Object[] {SecurityActionsTest.class},\\n                    TestClass.class,\\n                    TestClass.class.getClassLoader());\\n\\n            assertThat(created.getJavaClass()).isSameAs(SecurityActionsTest.class);\\n            assertThat(created.getName()).isEqualTo(SecurityActionsTest.class.getName());\\n        } finally {\\n            Thread.currentThread().setContextClassLoader(originalContextClassLoader);\\n        }\\n    }\\n\\n    private static final class HidingClassLoader extends ClassLoader {\\n        private final String hiddenClassName;\\n\\n        private HidingClassLoader(ClassLoader parent, String hiddenClassName) {\\n            super(parent);\\n            this.hiddenClassName = hiddenClassName;\\n        }\\n\\n        @Override\\n        protected Class<?> loadClass(String name, boolean resolve) throws ClassNotFoundException {\\n            if (hiddenClassName.equals(name)) {\\n                throw new ClassNotFoundException(name);\\n            }\\n            return super.loadClass(name, resolve);\\n        }\\n    }\\n}\\n\"}\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.jboss.arquillian.test:arquillian-test-spi:1.1.10.Final/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-04T01-29-51-720954Z.log:1339:[tool-call] end id=call_0O90FpD3pzJbVRJjp2YnU5hR|fc_062975e28a80f5970169f7f6509be4819c877f88fb2d7cefa8 name=write args={\"path\": \"tests/src/org.jboss.arquillian.test/arquillian-test-spi/1.1.10.Final/src/test/java/org_jboss_arquillian_test/arquillian_test_spi/SecurityActionsTest.java\", \"content\": \"/*\\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\\n *\\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\\n */\\npackage org_jboss_arquillian_test.arquillian_test_spi;\\n\\nimport static org.assertj.core.api.Assertions.assertThat;\\n\\nimport org.jboss.arquillian.test.spi.SecurityActionsInvoker;\\nimport org.jboss.arquillian.test.spi.TestClass;\\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\\n\\npublic class SecurityActionsTest {\\n    @Test\\n    void loadsClassesAndCreatesInstancesThroughSecurityActions() {\\n        ClassLoader originalContextClassLoader = Thread.currentThread().getContextClassLoader();\\n        String testClassName = TestClass.class.getName();\\n\\n        try {\\n            Thread.currentThread().setContextClassLoader(TestClass.class.getClassLoader());\\n            assertThat(SecurityActionsInvoker.loadClass(testClassName)).isSameAs(TestClass.class);\\n\\n            Thread.currentThread().setContextClassLoader(new HidingClassLoader(TestClass.class.getClassLoader(), testClassName));\\n            assertThat(SecurityActionsInvoker.loadClass(testClassName)).isSameAs(TestClass.class);\\n\\n            TestClass created = SecurityActionsInvoker.newInstance(\\n                    testClassName,\\n                    new Class<?>[] {Class.class},\\n                    new Object[] {SecurityActionsTest.class},\\n                    TestClass.class,\\n                    TestClass.class.getClassLoader());\\n\\n            assertThat(created.getJavaClass()).isSameAs(SecurityActionsTest.class);\\n            assertThat(created.getName()).isEqualTo(SecurityActionsTest.class.getName());\\n        } finally {\\n            Thread.currentThread().setContextClassLoader(originalContextClassLoader);\\n        }\\n    }\\n\\n    private static final class HidingClassLoader extends ClassLoader {\\n        private final String hiddenClassName;\\n\\n        private HidingClassLoader(ClassLoader parent, String hiddenClassName) {\\n            super(parent);\\n            this.hiddenClassName = hiddenClassName;\\n        }\\n\\n        @Override\\n        protected Class<?> loadClass(String name, boolean resolve) throws ClassNotFoundException {\\n            if (hiddenClassName.equals(name)) {\\n                throw new ClassNotFoundException(name);\\n            }\\n            return super.loadClass(name, resolve);\\n        }\\n    }\\n}\\n\"}\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.jboss.arquillian.test:arquillian-test-spi:1.1.10.Final/add-new-library-support/pi-genera